### ========================================
### 浏览历史功能测试文件
### ========================================

### 基础配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userId = 1
@contentType = knowledge
@contentId = 1

### ========================================
### 1. 创建浏览记录
### ========================================

### 1.1 创建知识浏览记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "knowledge",
  "contentId": 1,
  "title": "常见网络诈骗类型识别",
  "summary": "了解常见的网络诈骗类型，提高防范意识"
}

###

### 1.2 创建案例浏览记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "case",
  "contentId": 1,
  "title": "冒充客服诈骗案例",
  "summary": "某市民接到冒充客服电话被骗10万元"
}

###

### 1.3 创建帖子浏览记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "post",
  "contentId": 1,
  "title": "分享我的防诈骗经验",
  "summary": "今天差点被骗，分享给大家"
}

###

### 1.4 批量创建浏览记录（用于测试分页）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "knowledge",
  "contentId": 2,
  "title": "电信诈骗防范指南",
  "summary": "学习如何识别和防范电信诈骗"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "knowledge",
  "contentId": 3,
  "title": "投资诈骗警示",
  "summary": "高收益投资往往是诈骗陷阱"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "case",
  "contentId": 2,
  "title": "网络贷款诈骗案例",
  "summary": "轻信网络贷款广告，被骗5万元"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "case",
  "contentId": 3,
  "title": "刷单诈骗案例",
  "summary": "参与刷单兼职，被骗3万元"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "post",
  "contentId": 2,
  "title": "如何识别虚假投资平台",
  "summary": "分享识别虚假投资平台的方法"
}

###

### ========================================
### 2. 获取用户的所有浏览记录
### ========================================

### 2.1 获取用户ID为1的所有浏览记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1

###

### 2.2 获取用户ID为2的所有浏览记录（如果存在）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/2

###

### ========================================
### 3. 分页获取用户的浏览记录
### ========================================

### 3.1 获取第1页，每页10条记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/page?page=1&size=10

###

### 3.2 获取第2页，每页5条记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/page?page=2&size=5

###

### 3.3 获取第1页，每页3条记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/page?page=1&size=3

###

### ========================================
### 4. 按内容类型获取用户的浏览记录
### ========================================

### 4.1 获取用户的知识浏览记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/type/knowledge

###

### 4.2 获取用户的案例浏览记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/type/case

###

### 4.3 获取用户的帖子浏览记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/type/post

###

### ========================================
### 5. 获取用户最近浏览的记录
### ========================================

### 5.1 获取用户最近浏览的10条记录（默认）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/recent

###

### 5.2 获取用户最近浏览的5条记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/recent?limit=5

###

### 5.3 获取用户最近浏览的3条记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/recent?limit=3

###

### ========================================
### 6. 统计用户的浏览次数
### ========================================

### 6.1 统计用户ID为1的总浏览次数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/count

###

### 6.2 统计用户ID为2的总浏览次数（如果存在）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/2/count

###

### ========================================
### 7. 统计用户对指定内容的浏览次数
### ========================================

### 7.1 统计用户对知识ID为1的浏览次数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/count/content?contentType=knowledge&contentId=1

###

### 7.2 统计用户对案例ID为1的浏览次数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/count/content?contentType=case&contentId=1

###

### 7.3 统计用户对帖子ID为1的浏览次数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/count/content?contentType=post&contentId=1

###

### ========================================
### 8. 删除浏览记录
### ========================================

### 8.1 删除指定ID的浏览记录（需要先查询获取ID）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/1

###

### 8.2 删除另一个浏览记录
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/2

###

### ========================================
### 9. 删除用户的所有浏览记录
### ========================================

### 9.1 删除用户ID为1的所有浏览记录
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1

###

### 9.2 删除用户ID为2的所有浏览记录（如果存在）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/2

###

### ========================================
### 10. 综合测试场景
### ========================================

### 10.1 完整的用户浏览流程测试
### 步骤1：创建浏览记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "knowledge",
  "contentId": 1,
  "title": "测试知识",
  "summary": "测试摘要"
}

###

### 步骤2：查询浏览记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1

###

### 步骤3：统计浏览次数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/count

###

### 步骤4：获取最近浏览记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/recent?limit=5

###

### 步骤5：按类型查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1/type/knowledge

###

### 10.2 多用户浏览记录测试
### 用户1创建浏览记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "contentType": "knowledge",
  "contentId": 1,
  "title": "用户1浏览的知识",
  "summary": "用户1的浏览记录"
}

###

### 用户2创建浏览记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "contentType": "knowledge",
  "contentId": 1,
  "title": "用户2浏览的知识",
  "summary": "用户2的浏览记录"
}

###

### 分别查询两个用户的浏览记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/1

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/learning-records/user/2

###

